data.description: Great home available in Bear Valley Springs. This unique property has plenty of amenities, and privacy for the family. The interior features a multi level design, huge bonus room downstairs with  bathroom and even a secret room behind the bookshelf. The kitchen and bathrooms have been updated, and has all the modern updates one could want combined with that rustic bear valley design. The exterior features additional storage shed, multiple balconies, and newer roof with over one acre of land. The bear valley association also comes with plenty of amenities including country club, lakes, golf course, and much more. Make your appointment today
